📖 活動簡介

📖 About the Event

《流通經營者高峰論壇》為台灣連鎖暨加盟協會（TCFA）年度指標盛會，已邁入第 24 屆。本屆以「創新迎變、創造新局」為主軸，聚焦零售與通路的數位轉型、會員經營與跨域合作；車麗屋由董事長卓豐閔分享「服務多元創新：車後市場生態系的打造」。

The TCFA Retail Entrepreneur Summit is the association’s annual flagship event. Now in its 24th year, it focuses on digital transformation, omni‑channel operations, and membership strategies. Car1 Chairman Feng Min Cho presented “Service Innovation: Building an Auto‑Aftermarket Ecosystem.”

  • 主辦單位：台灣連鎖暨加盟協會（TCFA）
  • 時間：2025 年 9 月 24 日
  • 地點：台北
  • Organizer: TCFA
  • Date: Sep 24, 2025
  • Venue: Taipei

🎤 簡報重點

🎤 Talk Highlights

企業版圖Group

汽車百貨、商場、停車場與保險經紀多元事業；以車後服務為核心。

Diverse businesses—auto retail, malls, parking, insurance—centered on the auto‑aftermarket.

發展里程碑Milestones

1994 首店 → 2000 成立 → 2003 ISO → 2016 SAP/O2O → 2021 台鐵案 → 2024 國家品質獎、攜手 Point S。

1994 first store → 2000 founded → 2003 ISO → 2016 SAP/O2O → 2021 TRA project → 2024 National Quality Award & Point S partnership.

會員經營Membership

180 萬會員、HappyGo 合作；整合人車履歷與消費歷程，推動個人化行銷。

1.8M members with HappyGo; unified people‑car profiles & journeys enable personalization.

數位三支柱Digital Trio

雲端 POS、智慧選品 Web、對話式商務 LineBot（貨價查詢）。

Cloud POS, smart assortment web, and conversational LineBot for price lookup.

數據中台Data Platform

整合會員/商品/場域/供應商/車輛/員工 ID，串接 POS/EIP/SAP ERP，驅動採購、庫存、財會、KPI。

Integrates member/product/location/supplier/vehicle/staff IDs with POS/EIP/SAP to drive purchasing, inventory, finance, and KPIs.

🛒 全通路事業版圖

🛒 Omni‑channel Footprint

線下據點Offline
直營通路 33 店、台亞加油站 111 站。 33 directly‑operated stores; 111 Formosa Gas Station locations in collaboration.
線上據點Online
自營 O2O 官網 + 各大電商平台；24/7 服務。 O2O website plus marketplaces; 24/7 service.
全球合作Global
Point S 遍及 5 大洲、53 國、6500 銷售點。 Point S across 5 continents, 53 countries, and 6,500 points of sale.

🧠 數位轉型與系統整合

🧠 Digital & Systems

  • POS：收銀、採購、庫存、會員、美容、保險整合管理
  • EIP：出缺勤、排班、KPI、公文、ISO 品管
  • SAP ERP：日結自動拋帳；BI 追蹤客單價、來客數、銷售趨勢
  • POS: cashiering, purchasing, inventory, membership, grooming, insurance
  • EIP: attendance, scheduling, KPIs, documents, ISO QMS
  • SAP ERP: daily postings; BI dashboards for AOV, traffic, sales trends

🧭 OMO 會員策略

🧭 OMO & CRM

  • Line／App 與門市、官網整合，建立虛實互動與個人化優惠
  • 會員數據串接：人車履歷 + 消費歷程，精準行銷與回購
  • 通路導購：線上下單、到店安裝，流程即時通知與回饋
  • Integrate Line/App with stores and web for personalized offers
  • Unified people‑car profiles and purchase journeys for precision marketing
  • O2O: order online, install in‑store, with real‑time notifications and feedback

🚀 未來拓展

🚀 Future Expansion

  • 新商品領域：寵物用品、露營用品、機車部品
  • 國際合作：攜手 Point S，立足台灣、鏈結全球供應鏈
  • 生態擴張：B2B/B2C 並進，供應鏈 500+ 協力廠商共創
  • New Product Segments: pet supplies, camping gear, motorcycle parts
  • International Partner: Point S—rooted in Taiwan, connected worldwide
  • Ecosystem Expansion: B2B & B2C in parallel with 500+ partner suppliers
